  Name: Debuff
  Type: Impact
  Icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6c0c6d4441efb23498999e07ee72e378, type: 3}
  Description: "Applies a debuff based on the spell\u2019s elemental type for 5 seconds.
    This effect does not stack, but increases in strength with additional Debuff
    Runes. \nFire: Reduces ATK\nWater: Reduces Speed\nThunder: Reduces ATKSPD\nEarth:
    Reduces Healing received\nNeutral: Reduces a random stat mentioned above\nAn
    enemy may be affected by many debuffs of the same type as long as they are from
    different elements. The debuff will reapply with each impact, resetting its duration."
  _duration: 5
